<a name="API_wafRegional_GetLoggingConfiguration_ResponseElements"></a>

If the action is successful, the service sends back an HTTP 200 response.

The following data is returned in JSON format by the service.

 ** [LoggingConfiguration](#API_wafRegional_GetLoggingConfiguration_ResponseSyntax) **   <a name="WAF-wafRegional_GetLoggingConfiguration-response-LoggingConfiguration"></a>
The [LoggingConfiguration](API_wafRegional_LoggingConfiguration.md) for the specified web ACL.  
